@Node "History"

@{b}@{u}History:@{uu}@{ub}

1.0  - First release.

1.01 - Changed the window title from "Calc" to "IntCalc".
     - Added a screen title.
     - The multiplication did not work correctly when the result
       overflowed the long word range.
     - The shifting operations did not work correctly in certain cases.
     - Now the keys not available depending on the current base are
       disabled.
     - There were problems when two or more IntCalc's were running at
       the same time.
     - Some other minor changes.

1.1  - Added memory functions.
     - Now the buttons size fit the screen font with more accuracy.
     - Another minor change.


@Endnode
